<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/17906236-robin-card"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1362051860i/17906236._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/17906236-robin-card">Robin Card</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
It was originally published in London, hence the Anglo-centric nature of the book and the frequent reference to British peers.
</span>
</div>
