<div id="review_3308382986" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3308382986" />
    <a title="Connor" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/111933447-connor"><img alt="Connor" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1587750743p2/111933447.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3308382986?book_show_action=true">Apr 29, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Connor" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Connor" href="/user/show/111933447-connor">Connor</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780415253895" href="/book/show/6290.The_Road_to_Serfdom">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3308382986" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3318500978174426502">This was utter garbage. This was the lowest point of intellectual history; it combined selfish morals with so-called &apos;logic&apos; and used distorted arguments to justify libertarian capitalism that whenever tried has led to starvation and the deaths of thousands. What is clear from his writings is that Hayek was a dick. He was even worse than his successor Milton Friedman and that is saying a lot! All these so-called libertarian economists prove by their stupid books and arguments is that they just w</span>
  <span id="freeText3318500978174426502" style="display:none">This was utter garbage. This was the lowest point of intellectual history; it combined selfish morals with so-called 'logic' and used distorted arguments to justify libertarian capitalism that whenever tried has led to starvation and the deaths of thousands. What is clear from his writings is that Hayek was a dick. He was even worse than his successor Milton Friedman and that is saying a lot! All these so-called libertarian economists prove by their stupid books and arguments is that they just want to justify with any means their insatiable desire for money. I am not supporting communism or socialism for that matter by expressing my hatred of this book; in fact any one who actually cares about people should rightfully hate this literal piece of trash. Unfortunately the publishers of this book failed to recognise this and now this piece of trash is out in the world and sadly it will influence people to support these crooked 'ideas' of the political economist Hayek.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3318500978174426502" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


